videos.headline: Idaho strikes first for TD
videos.description: Matt Linehan hits David Ungerer for a 26-yard touchdown pass play to put Idaho on the board.

videos.headline: Hall capitalizes on tip drill interception for Idaho
videos.description: Ed Hall interception off the deflection of teammate sets up the Vandals.

videos.headline: Duckworth power display for TD
videos.description: Aaron Duckworth runs for a 6-yard touchdown to increase the lead for Idaho.

videos.headline: Evans finds Pederson to set up Louisiana Monroe
videos.description: Caleb Evans connets with Josh Pederson for a 26-yard pass play to set up 1st and goal for Louisiana Monroe

videos.headline: Idaho stymies Louisiana Monroe at the goal line
videos.description: Derrick Gore runs for no gain on 4th and goal at the Idaho goal line

videos.headline: Linehan to Elliss for TD pads the lead for Idaho
videos.description: Matt Linehan finds Kaden Ellis for a 45-yard touchdown pass to increase the lead to 21 in the 2nd quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_Idaho Final Game Highlight (Linehan to Elliss for TD pads the lead for Idaho) 2017/10/28

videos.headline: Evans and Gillespie combine for a big play TD for Louisiana Monroe
videos.description: Caleb Evans finds D'Marius Gillespie for a 54-yard touchdown pass to put Louisiana Monroe on the board.

videos.headline: Idaho's Ungerer sliding catch puts the Vandals in Louisiana Monroe territory
videos.description: David Ungerer's sliding 29-yard catch sets up Idaho in for another score.

videos.headline: Linehan's third TD pass pushes the lead for Idaho
videos.description: Matt Linehan hits Alfonso Onunwor for a 11-yard touchdown pass to add to the lead for Idaho.

videos.headline: Linehan to Mwehla puts Idaho in Louisiana Monroe territory
videos.description: Matt Linehan finds Reuben Mwehla for a 40 yard pass play that would lead to a Idaho field goal.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe TD cuts into the Idaho lead.
videos.description: Calab Evans connects with  Brian Williams for a 26-yard touchdown to cut the deficit for Louisiana Monroe.

videos.headline: Johnson and Henderson bottles up Idaho on 4th down
videos.description: Idaho's Isaiah Saunders is stop behind the line on 4th down by Louisiana Monroe's Tyler Johnson and DJ Henderson that would lead to a Louisiana Monroe field goal.

videos.headline: Evans connects with Turner for a big-time pass completion
videos.description: Caleb Evans escapes a pass rusher and finds RJ Turner for a 27-yard pass play to set up Louisiana Monroe deep in Idaho territory.

videos.headline: Evans' third TD pass closes the gap for Louisiana Monroe
videos.description: Caleb Evans finds Derrick Gore for a 13-yard touchdown, which cuts the Idaho lead to 8 late in the fourth quarter.
